	(text "Hall sensing - Uses magnetic field to induce proportional current\nNo Shunt Resistor\nRejects Common Mode\nSuppressing output noise\nBandwidth 120khz\n\nFilter pin adjustments - better resolution in lower f\n\nAEC-Q100 - automotive graded "
